{"tid":2383513,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"貓仔做絕育 姑娘誤叫我隻貓禁食成21個鐘","createTime":"2021-01-28T03:03:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T07:19:04.000Z","uid":119100,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8ba5d4fe9f7c8bd923428fa3adbe2d1922372c51","tid":2383513,"uid":119100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T03:03:50.000Z","msg":"早兩個星期打左去馬鞍山間獸醫book 朝早9:30絕育手術<br />\n個姑娘話要前一日中午12點開始禁食<br />\n我都心諗下要咁耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我就問佢：要咁耐架？我想問其實係exactly幾多個鐘？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個姑娘：er總之就中午12點半開始禁啦<br />\n<br />\n屋企人其實都有懷疑過 見上網睇都係講禁8個鐘左右 咁我緊係信診所多過上網啦 我咪諗住可能禁耐啲就唔會手術嘔到啲野食 make sure胃腸都空<br />\n<br />\n而手術前一日姑娘都再打電話黎double confirm 肯定佢話中午12點開始禁食<br />\n<br />\n屌 今朝去到診所 有幾個姑娘返工 其中一個問我幾點開始禁食 我就話中午12點<br />\n<br />\n跟住個姑娘就話 下咁貓仔咪餓左好耐？<br />\n<br />\n我就講番姑娘同我電話講既野比佢知<br />\n跟住其他姑娘都唔sure要禁幾耐 問黎問去 問番醫生最後都話應該係夜晚12點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嬲到傻 同埋勁心痛自己隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n心諗佢地連絕育咁基本既手術 佢地都唔知禁食時間<br />\n好流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見醫生打針問佢打咩針又唔鬼答<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住到成4點先可以接貓 咁佢就會餓左成28個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為有親戚同事既寵物都睇開呢間獸醫<br />\n所以我先睇呢間<br />\n<br />\n有冇沙田區既獸醫好介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"544f47a9201214fc23dc0dad963f411cd607e3bb","tid":2383513,"uid":196692,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T03:13:26.000Z","msg":"28小時冇乜問題既...成年貓2日唔食野都頂到"},{"pid":"d877f0db2ac87195ee4cb77f6ad425815269677c","tid":2383513,"uid":375032,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T03:16:04.000Z","msg":"點解幾個診所姑娘都答唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全部新人黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f2f37e569a1f046b3331ed519ac0e2b614374b","tid":2383513,"uid":364850,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T03:37:44.000Z","msg":"好可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"628d0bc9ac7ec988b9c2ac9904f9cd7da29d5016","tid":2383513,"uid":119100,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"544f47a9201214fc23dc0dad963f411cd607e3bb","tid":2383513,"uid":196692,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T03:13:26.000Z","msg":"28小時冇乜問題既...成年貓2日唔食野都頂到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T07:40:23.000Z","msg":"但承受左不必要的苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人餓咁耐都辛苦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91db22dedb3298659ed83892da63ca110bc641d8","tid":2383513,"uid":322690,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T16:15:03.000Z","msg":"邊間😱 白色屋苑 /紅色屋苑5期/紅色屋苑1期<br />\n就嚟養貓，諗住睇紅色屋苑1期嗰間"},{"pid":"46ba61141a366c360fff0e4e266989242b1da25f","tid":2383513,"uid":379710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T18:07:05.000Z","msg":"大圍俊康闕醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69d5655253747cd5e6342266d2e890411920ca14","tid":2383513,"uid":119100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91db2